Package connectfour

The connectfour package is the main package in the Connect Four program.
Author:
elliot gorman
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CirclePanel
    The panels which the circles are drawn on (when clicked).
    ConnectFour
    The Main class, builds the GUI, then dispatches the GUI in the main method.
    GameData
    The gameData class which stores all game data such as the board and the current player.
    GridPane
    The grid component which houses all the pieces.
    SerializeSystem
    The "save" system of the game serializes and un-serializes values.
